a simple spider to spide www.wxianfeng.cn

this is a demo , how to use ruby code a spider to spide web page , if u download source 

just run  ruby spider_wxianfeng_cn_main.rb in shell

then u can find backup file(html) under folder file 

and blog's images will save in  images folder

